<br>
as to getting people flagged for these areas who missed the guild raid...this is quite simple, do the raid again.  unless you won completely by luck it will be much easier the second time around.  or, if you're talking about the poj trials...then you're gonna be doing them over and over and over anyway, so once more is no big deal.<br>
